reviews.reviewText: This is a nice bulk set available at a fair price (currently listed for $9.99/150 pc, $0.07/pc). All the pieces look clean & aren't scratched, which is more than I can say for other sets I've ordered. They are sturdy & can withstand a lot, we have yet to have a piece snap on us.I used these while hosting Christmas Eve dinner so they were certainly put to the test & we had no issues whatsoever. It's a good sized pack to have on hand for day to day use (especially with kids) or when hosting (yay! less dishes), I recommend it either way.
